STL TECHNOLOGY C said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 67.64% to NT$184,349,000 from NT$569,608,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            184,349          569,608    
YOY%             -67.64%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            842,780         1,979,536   
YOY%             -57.43% 
=================================================================
 